The paper discusses the use of cloud middleware platforms and tools for IoT data analytics tasks, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also focuses on data processing and analytics, which is related to Databases (cs.DB) and Cybersecurity and Privacy (cs.CY). The paper proposes an architecture for a system, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
